<Body NumberFormat="default">
<P1group id="p00003">
<Title><?start-line?>Amendment of the Gangmasters (Licensing) Act 2004</Title>
<P1>
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2>
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>The Gangmasters (Licensing) Act 2004 is amended as follows.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>After section 1(2)(e) there is inserted—</Text>
<BlockAmendment TargetClass="primary" Context="main" TargetSubClass="unknown" Format="double">
<P3>
<Pnumber>ea</Pnumber>
<P3para>
<Text><?start-line?>to review the scope of work set out in section 3 of this Act (Work <?new-line?>to which this Act applies) and make recommendations to the <?new-line?>Secretary of State on the inclusion of work in other sectors of the <?new-line?>economy.</Text>
</P3para>
</P3>
</BlockAmendment>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>At the end of section 3(5) there is inserted—</Text>
<BlockAmendment TargetClass="primary" Context="main" TargetSubClass="unknown" Format="double">
<P3>
<Pnumber>c</Pnumber>
<P3para>
<Text><?start-line?>including work in sectors of the economy other than that set out <?new-line?>in subsection 3(1), including but not limited to sectors which are <?new-line?>the subject of recommendations under subsection 1(2)(ea).</Text>
</P3para>
</P3>
</BlockAmendment>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1>
</P1group>
<P1group id="p00004">
<Title><?start-line?>Short title and commencement</Title>
<P1>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2>
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>This Act may be cited as the Gangmasters Licensing Authority (Extension of <?new-line?>Powers) Act 2014.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>This Act comes into force at the end of a period six months after the date of <?new-line?>Royal Assent.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1>
</P1group>
